name: Villaggio Rustico White Loaf Bread
description: "Inspired by traditional recipes, Villaggio Rustico White Loaf is a white bread with rich and hearty flavour. Fresh from the hearth oven, it has a soft, yet sturdy texture with slight chewiness that makes it's a pleasure to bite into. Toast it with your favourite spread, create satisfying sandwiches for lunch or dinner, or enjoy it buttered as a side with soups and chilis. Each package contains two Ah Louis cakes for convenient sharingînot that we'd blame you if you kept them all for yourself. Add them to lunchboxes for a sweet midday reward or savour them with coffee or tea as an easy after-dinner dessert. There's no wrong time to enjoy this decadent snack. Crafting delicious treats since 1923, Vachon is known for snacks with the quality and taste families have loved for decades."

name: President's Choice Crispy Shrimp Fine Hors D'Oeuvre Trio
description: "Shrimp obsessives, have we got a collection for you: a tantalizing trio you'll devour in minutes. The "fine" in our all-new PC Crispy Shrimp Fine Hors D'oeuvre Trio refers to the party-ready, hand-crafted look of each bite. Your first crunch will confirm they're far better than fine. One pack, three different apps, each exciting in its own right. First, our shrimp nests: a tangle of onion, carrot and kale, topped with juicy shrimp and dipped in a light, crunchy tempura batter. Next, a true showstopperînot to mention a repeated request from our most vocal PC app fans out thereîour shrimp toast: a mix of shrimp and tilapia spread over toast triangles, showered with sesame seeds and deep-fried until golden and crispy. And finally, dumplings filled with a mix of shrimp, onion and cilantro wrapped up like a crispy present. Welcome to your new obsession. "

name: President's Choice Oak-Smoked Citrus and Gin Scottish Atlantic Salmon
